column5: As you all know from silveradosherriffs report we finished the weekend in 12th position. Saturday was great, but really had to work hard for them today.  Here's some pics.                           Thanks again guys for a great weekend.  (still get goosebumps looking at the pics of blastoff!!)
do people actually eat those or are the pics just glory shots?
Good job buddy! Those are some nice fish.
Looks like you gave it ur best and came out with some VERY nice fish. Good job boys.
congrats on the good finish  and to clarify for those wondering, none of the fish were wasted
